name: Wynona Fitzgerald: A Milwaukee Adventure (Sad Goose Cooperative)
name_original: Wynona Fitzgerald: A Milwaukee Adventure (Sad Goose Cooperative)
description:
You are ordinary accountant Wynona Fitzgerald.

Explore Milwaukee. Touch a poisonous frog. Date your coworkers. Remake the world in your image, as though you were a god.

Written by Luke Hauge and Clair Willden for Sad Goose Cooperative
